    base:desc "The digital shadow constellation consists of a Purpose element (FrictionDerivation), an Asset element (the first axis of the MABI robot), Processing components (Simulation_M, Simulation_GW, Simulation_GB) that consume input data traces and produce simulated outputs, and various DataTrace and DataPoint instances (I_M, r_M, r_G, r_out, ˆr_M, ˆr_G, ˆr_out) linked to their Sources and Models."
