instance dt_technical_connection : DTDFVocab:TechnicalConnection [
    base:desc "Data are transmitted from the robot to the digital shadow over MQTT, establishing a one‑way automated data flow as defined for digital shadows. Asset Administration Shells are used to bind the physical asset metadata with the virtual models."
